---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about Jack Squire - Founder, entrepreneur, and builder of products."
>
  <section class="section pt-32 md:pt-40">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <!-- Header with Photo -->
      <div class="mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center md:items-start">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="relative flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-purple-500 to-secondary rounded-2xl blur-lg opacity-40"></div>
          <div class="relative w-48 h-48 md:w-56 md:h-56 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-white/10">
            <img
              src="/images/jack-about.jpg"
              alt="Jack Squire"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Text -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">
            About Me
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Founder, entrepreneur, and eternal optimist who believes the best way
            to predict the future is to build it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="prose-custom">
        <h2>The Short Version</h2>
        <p>
          I'm Jack Squire, a founder and entrepreneur based in [Your Location]. I spend my days
          building products, writing about what I learn, and helping other founders navigate
          the chaos of building something from nothing.
        </p>

        <h2>The Longer Version</h2>
        <p>
          My journey into entrepreneurship started when I realized I was better at creating
          solutions than following instructions. What began as tinkering with side projects
          evolved into a full-blown obsession with building things that matter.
        </p>
        <p>
          Over the years, I've launched multiple products, experienced the highs of successful
          launches and the lows of spectacular failures. Each venture taught me something new
          about product development, user psychology, and the art of perseverance.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, I focus on building sustainable businesses that solve real problems for real
          people. I believe in shipping fast, iterating based on feedback, and never being
          too attached to my own ideas.
        </p>

        <h2>What I Believe In</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Ship early, ship often.</strong> Perfect is the enemy of shipped.</li>
          <li><strong>Talk to users.</strong> The best product insights come from real conversations.</li>
          <li><strong>Stay curious.</strong> The best founders are perpetual learners.</li>
          <li><strong>Share openly.</strong> Knowledge grows when shared.</li>
          <li><strong>Focus relentlessly.</strong> Say no to almost everything to say yes to what matters.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Beyond Work</h2>
        <p>
          When I'm not building or writing, you'll find me reading (mostly non-fiction and
          sci-fi), exploring new places, or diving deep into whatever rabbit hole has
          captured my attention that week. I'm endlessly fascinated by how things work
          and why people do what they do.
        </p>

        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
        <p>
          I love meeting new people and hearing about what you're building. Whether you
          want to collaborate, ask questions, or just say hello, don't hesitate to reach out.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <Button href="mailto:hello@jacksquire.com">
          Send me an email
        </Button>
        <Button href="https://twitter.com/jacksquire" variant="secondary" external>
          Follow on Twitter
        </Button>
        <Button href="https://linkedin.com/in/jacksquire" variant="secondary" external>
          Connect on LinkedIn
        </Button>
      </div>

      <!-- Fun Facts -->
      <div class="mt-16 pt-16 border-t border-border">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-8">Quick Facts</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="card text-center p-4">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">‚òï</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">Coffee Enthusiast</div>
          </div>
